Dream trees are trees found in the Dream World during the Lunar Diplomacy quest. The trees yield dream logs which are used during one of the challenges in the quest. Players can cut these trees at level 55 Woodcutting but cannot fletch or burn the logs from them. The logs acquired from these trees cannot be taken from outside the Dream World.

If attempting to chop the tree during the fight against Me, a chatbox with the message: "Now is now the time!" appears.

Players can cut these trees at level 55 [[Woodcutting]] but cannot fletch or burn the logs from them. The logs acquired from these trees cannot be taken from outside the [[Dream World]].

If attempting to chop the tree during the fight against [[Me]], a chatbox with the message: "Now is now the time!" appears.
